long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An unofficial collection of dark styles for UTwente websites. 
Supported websites:
- Canvas
- Horus
- Osiris
- Printportal
- Printquota
- BigBlueButton
- Rooster
- Signon

Extra functionality:
- Fixes a few breaking bugs on pages
- Tries to replace the Canvas video player with Plyr

Not affiliated with the University of Twente in any way.
